summary: Taking a brief break from DELTARUNE SPAM to draw some kids from My Hero Academia.  My brother’s really active in the fandom and...
caption:
Taking a brief break from DELTARUNE SPAM to draw some kids from My Hero Academia. 

My brother’s really active in the fandom and has been trying to get me to read the manga for quite a while now. It was only after he bought One’s Justice for the Switch that I decided to give it a try - I wanted to actually have some idea of who these strange anime people in the game were.  

As it turns out, I actually like the manga a lot. I’ve finished the first six volumes and will be starting the seventh soon. Currently, these six dorks are among my favourite characters. (I also really like Thirteen and Kurogiri. Shoji is also slowly growing on me, mostly because I like characters with multiple arms. I may draw them sometime.)

The DELTARUNE SPAM will resume shortly.

question: Setsuna?
answer:
This is literally the oldest ask here and it’s from before I became a Mod, so I’m 99% sure it’s from the “send me a character and I’ll give you these specific headcanons” prompt.

So let’s do it. Good lizard girl is best.

Sexuality Headcanon: Pansexual/bisexual

Gender Headcanon: Female

A ship I have with said character: X Rin, X Yanagi, X Habuko (honestly anyone)

A BROTP I have with said character: Kendo, Yanagi, Mina

A NOTP I have with said character: she can go with anyone IMO, but I’ll just say Monoma for now

A random headcanon: a massive flirt that has come onto almost all of her classmates at least once. He favorite targets are Rin, Yanagi, and Kendo.

General opinion over said character: I love her with all my heart 💜

- Mod Iron
